dc_description_s: These polygon data layers represent land use for La Crosse County, Wisconsin in 2013. It is a feature class within the geodatabase LaCrosse_LandUse_2013.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'LA_CROSSE_LANDUSE_EXISTING_2013' and 'LA_CROSSE_LANDUSE_FUTURE_2013'.
